text: Aleksey Sinkevich (born 10 June 1977) is a Belarusian gymnast. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Vitebsk
